---
// Temporary mockup - DELETE after design approval
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Modules - Accordion</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap');

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; background: #0a0a0a; color: #fff; }

    .section-header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 80px 20px 50px;
    }
    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .section-header h2 span { color: #e74c3c; }
    .section-header p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
      font-size: 1rem;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .accordion-wrap {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 20px 80px;
    }

    .acc-item {
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .acc-item:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }

    .acc-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 22px 0;
    }

    .acc-thumb {
      width: 80px;
      height: 56px;
      min-width: 80px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      object-fit: cover;
      opacity: 0.5;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .acc-item.active .acc-thumb,
    .acc-item:hover .acc-thumb { opacity: 1; }

    .acc-num {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.2);
      min-width: 50px;
      line-height: 1;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }
    .acc-item.active .acc-num { color: #e74c3c; }

    .acc-text { flex: 1; }
    .acc-title {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .acc-sub {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    }

    .acc-arrow {
      margin-left: auto;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      transition: all 0.3s;
      min-width: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .acc-item.active .acc-arrow { transform: rotate(45deg); color: #e74c3c; }

    .acc-expand {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.4s ease, padding 0.3s ease;
      padding: 0 0 0 150px;
    }
    .acc-item.active .acc-expand {
      max-height: 300px;
      padding: 0 0 22px 150px;
    }

    .acc-topics { list-style: none; }
    .acc-topics li {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
      padding: 5px 0;
      padding-left: 18px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .acc-topics li::before {
      content: '+';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: #e74c3c;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .section-header h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
      .acc-thumb { width: 56px; height: 40px; min-width: 56px; border-radius: 8px; }
      .acc-num { font-size: 1.4rem; min-width: 36px; }
      .acc-title { font-size: 0.95rem; }
      .acc-expand { padding-left: 0 !important; }
      .acc-item.active .acc-expand { padding-left: 0 !important; }
      .acc-topics { padding-left: 92px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="section-header">
    <h2>What You'll <span>Master</span></h2>
    <p>7 modules. 30+ lessons. Everything you need to nail your low end.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="accordion-wrap">
    <div class="acc-item active">
      <div class="acc-header">
        <img class="acc-thumb" src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/BauKxvLpQYqLoxR7j01z_low+end+1+copy.jpg" alt="" />
        <div class="acc-num">01</div>
        <div class="acc-text">
          <div class="acc-title">Low End Theory - Fine-Tuning the Foundation</div>
          <div class="acc-sub">3 lessons</div>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-arrow">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc-expand">
        <ul class="acc-topics">
          <li>Why Low End Is So Important?</li>
          <li>Why Is It So Hard to Mix?</li>
          <li>FAQ & Common Mistakes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="acc-item">
      <div class="acc-header">
        <img class="acc-thumb" src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/5LOiP0Txl2oQno23I0gW_low+end.jpg" alt="" />
        <div class="acc-num">02</div>
        <div class="acc-text">
          <div class="acc-title">Navigating Tools and Challenges in Low-End Mixing</div>
          <div class="acc-sub">4 lessons</div>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-arrow">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc-expand">
        <ul class="acc-topics">
          <li>Your Ears</li>
          <li>Speakers & Room</li>
          <li>Headphones</li>
          <li>Metering</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="acc-item">
      <div class="acc-header">
        <img class="acc-thumb" src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/iduxgXajRo6h1LaC7Ahw_dQUY9H3oZvvbU7wsrJUyyvruMXwsYj8G2SdTfqv3+copy.jpg" alt="" />
        <div class="acc-num">03</div>
        <div class="acc-text">
          <div class="acc-title">Sound Sculpting - Techniques for the Perfect Kick</div>
          <div class="acc-sub">2 lessons</div>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-arrow">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc-expand">
        <ul class="acc-topics">
          <li>What Makes a Perfect Kick?</li>
          <li>Kick Shaping Examples (5 Demos)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="acc-item">
      <div class="acc-header">
        <img class="acc-thumb" src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/9GER2ESQpyYJYAdxuM3v_mono.jpg" alt="" />
        <div class="acc-num">04</div>
        <div class="acc-text">
          <div class="acc-title">All About The Bass - Achieving Bass Perfection</div>
          <div class="acc-sub">4 lessons</div>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-arrow">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc-expand">
        <ul class="acc-topics">
          <li>Saturation</li>
          <li>Mono-Compatibility</li>
          <li>Creating a Mono-Compatible Wide Bassline</li>
          <li>Note Selection</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="acc-item">
      <div class="acc-header">
        <img class="acc-thumb" src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/mQyIVU7NQEbQB6k6p4kA_sidechain.jpg" alt="" />
        <div class="acc-num">05</div>
        <div class="acc-text">
          <div class="acc-title">Kick Bass Chemistry - Decoding the Relationship</div>
          <div class="acc-sub">4 lessons</div>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-arrow">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc-expand">
        <ul class="acc-topics">
          <li>Kick & Bass - The Ideal Low End</li>
          <li>Dynamic Phase Rotation - Best Kept Secret</li>
          <li>Low-End Coherence</li>
          <li>Optimizing Kick and Bass in Mastering</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="acc-item">
      <div class="acc-header">
        <img class="acc-thumb" src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/aq3se6LNQkGTFfZVURXp_genre.jpg" alt="" />
        <div class="acc-num">06</div>
        <div class="acc-text">
          <div class="acc-title">Case Studies - Real-Life Examples</div>
          <div class="acc-sub">4 lessons</div>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-arrow">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc-expand">
        <ul class="acc-topics">
          <li>EDM Example</li>
          <li>Pop / Dance / Funk Example</li>
          <li>Trap / Hip Hop</li>
          <li>Reggaeton</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="acc-item">
      <div class="acc-header">
        <img class="acc-thumb" src="https://uploads.teachablecdn.com/attachments/Q5bGAEPwRXiGHIpphDVS_LOW+END+MASTERY.jpg" alt="" />
        <div class="acc-num">07</div>
        <div class="acc-text">
          <div class="acc-title">Bonus Lessons</div>
          <div class="acc-sub">4 lessons</div>
        </div>
        <div class="acc-arrow">+</div>
      </div>
      <div class="acc-expand">
        <ul class="acc-topics">
          <li>Spectre vs RBass or BassXXL</li>
          <li>Working Towards Loudness</li>
          <li>Low End Mastery Workshop (Live)</li>
          <li>Advanced Kick Shaping & Low End Control</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.acc-item').forEach(item => {
      item.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const wasActive = item.classList.contains('active');
        document.querySelectorAll('.acc-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('active'));
        if (!wasActive) item.classList.add('active');
      });
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
